{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the previous game, &quot;Christmas Blaster,&quot; Santa Claus had already faced and defeated Krampus, a malevolent creature that threatened Christmas. His courage and determination prevailed, restoring peace and joy. <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308050/extras/BANNER.png?t=1738326269\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Now, in &quot;Christmas Smash,&quot; Krampus returns, inciting a major rebellion among the elves and kidnapping Mrs. Claus with the intention of forcing Santa to abandon his mission. Santa Claus, known for his bravery and skills, is once again called upon to face the imminent danger and now also to save his beloved from Krampus and his army of renegade elves.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308050/extras/Vdeosemttulo-FeitocomClipchamp-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1738326269\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout the journey, Santa encounters dangerous challenges and formidable enemies, such as corrupted elves, machines, and ice soldiers. He relies on the help of his ally friends as he advances through snowy environments and even the lair of his enemy Krampus, confronting him in an epic final showdown.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308050/extras/gif_krmps.gif?t=1738326269\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready for an explosive, action-packed adventure!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308050/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738326269","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308050/page.bg.jpg?t=1738326269","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2308050/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738326269","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.st